title: Ep. 369 - Media and Hollywood Rally Behind Convicted Rapist and Murderer
description:
We take a look at the Rodney Reed case. Hollywood celebrities are rallying around him, but what facts are they leaving out? Also, a Canadian broadcaster was fired for innocuous comments about immigrants. Meanwhile, Justin Trudeau wore blackface and kept his job. Date: 11-12-2019
